{"tid":1431993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"百忙之中 不如笑下","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:29:16.000Z","uid":244765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c999ed3a381548e94889e000cf1a65cfc89ffd65","tid":1431993,"uid":244765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:23:39.000Z","msg":"話說小弟我尋日翻緊工個陣<br />\n有一枱客都係啲師奶嚟<br />\n聽得出佢地只喺淺黃<br />\n<br />\n其中有一段內容個陣真喺好難忍笑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />師奶1號   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />師奶2號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:尋日呀囡send咗張相俾我，入面個人着曬黑衫帶曬口罩咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:喺未啲示威者呀？啲後生雖然喺衝動，但喺佢地一直企喺前線幫我地爭取民主㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:起初我都唔知張相喺示威者嚟㗎，我仲以為喺唔知邊個韓星嚟咗香港。<br />\n<br />\n之後成枱笑到成間餐廳都聽到<br />\n而我聽到已經忍唔住要即刻跑入廚房笑陣先<br />\n心諗勇武派邊個咁靚仔可以做到韓星<br />\n<br />\n香港人輕鬆幾秒鐘先<br />\n之後先繼續錫人春袋啦。"},{"pid":"13eca814c54e3352fa1e3504c5b9680fffe3ecee","tid":1431993,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"做韓星唔洗生得靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}